 {
  "date": "Wed, 12 Jun 2013 10:48:29 GMT", 
  "link": "http://www.cnbeta.com/articles/240828.htm", 
  "description": "<b>美国谷歌公司在网络搜索和网络广告市场上的独大地位让欧盟感到担忧。欧盟官员最近指出，为了结束一项为期三年的反垄断调查，谷歌让步幅度应该更大，对其显示搜索结果的方式作出更多修改。</b>负责竞争事务的欧盟委员华金・阿尔穆尼亚不久前说，欧盟已决定将对谷歌反垄断和解提案的审议时间延长一个月。鉴于谷歌目前在和解提议中作出的让步并不能让各方满意，他几乎“百分之百”肯定，欧盟将对谷歌施加更大压力，要求该公司对和解提议作出改进。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2d2e8827/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240828.htm&amp;t=%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%81%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240828.htm&amp;t=%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%81%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240828.htm&amp;t=%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%81%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F240828.htm&amp;t=%E6%AC%A7%E7%9B%9F%EF%BC%9A%E8%B0%B7%E6%AD%8C%E5%BA%94%E5%AF%B9%E5%85%B6%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E5%81%9A%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9A%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http:/